data.description: OWNER MOTIVATED!!! This Energy Star Certified home has 4-bedrooms, 3 baths, covered lanai, 2-car garage on an elongated homesite with privacy fence in rear. Entertaining is a breeze with this open-concept layout. Kitchen features 42 espresso cabinets, stainless Whirlpool appliances, granite countertops and walk-in pantry. The Master Suite has a walk-in closet, dual sink vanity with granite counters, privacy lavatory, linen closet and garden bath with soaking tub a separate glass-enclosed shower. Located close to major highways, Orlando International Airport, Lake Nona, shops and dining. The Reserve at Sawgrass offers residents a Community Pool with Cabana, Playground, Sports Field and Dog Park.
